 ﻿Hello! Thanks for getting in touch via X&nbsp; 
 I’m looping in my client service manager Asher to share rates and business partner Sam Levin.&nbsp; 
 Asher/Sam this is a forwarded message from my X so you can have context of his ask.&nbsp; 
 “Hey! I’m Yihui from AD&amp;OG.




 We’re working with a new interactive AI story app where users can shape their own storylines, build relationships with characters, and explore different story outcomes based on their choices. 




 I came across your content and thought your style could be a really nice fit for this kind of campaign. Would you be open to hearing more about a possible collaboration? 




 If yes, feel free to share your rates or rate card, and I’ll send over more details. 😊” 



 Take it from here! All the best!&nbsp;


 Robert Scoble


